about you. Whit.

1369
01:06:59.220 --> 01:07:02.553
I'm sorry. I'm so tired.
I had the craziest day.

1370
01:07:02.553 --> 01:07:04.136
I just need to go to bed.

1371
01:07:05.470 --> 01:07:07.470
-Wait a bit.
-Come on. Colin.

1372
01:07:09.387 --> 01:07:10.720
[sighs]

1373
01:07:11.845 --> 01:07:13.679
