with me. Colin.

1377
01:07:26.887 --> 01:07:28.804
except for the fact
that my father just got

1378
01:07:28.804 --> 01:07:30.637
Harvey Weinstein'd.
and my whole future

1379
01:07:30.637 --> 01:07:32.887
