1396
01:08:49.595 --> 01:08:51.553
Furkat.

1397
01:08:51.553 --> 01:08:52.970
The photographer?

1398
01:08:52.970 --> 01:08:55.887
We used to date
back in New York.

1399
01:08:55.887 --> 01:08:57.220
What?

1400
